    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow an <strong>epic high fantasy story</strong> as you and your companions <strong>explore a world</strong> filled with quests and challenges that takes around <strong>20-30 hours</strong> to complete.<br><br>This game is <strong>not an auto-battler, nor is it a turn based tactics game</strong>. It's something in-between. But it is also a visual novel, where you follow quests and adventures and make choices.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/73aff832e25dba64078947d2bab012f9.poster.avif?t=1760778975\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/73aff832e25dba64078947d2bab012f9.webm?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/73aff832e25dba64078947d2bab012f9.mp4?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your party will go on <strong>adventures</strong>, fight <strong>battles</strong> and <strong>bosses</strong> to complete detailed and diverse quests, with a large variety of enemies. Each adventure is unique, but can be played a few different ways to give replayablility. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alot of the gameplay revolves arounds <strong>Guilds</strong> and the players reputation with them. Complete quests and sell loot to the guilds to gain reputation so to buy legendary weapons and hire new characters for your party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/7279cf3a0748cbab72a62bff14a0454a.poster.avif?t=1760778975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/7279cf3a0748cbab72a62bff14a0454a.webm?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/7279cf3a0748cbab72a62bff14a0454a.mp4?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each hero class has <strong>5 different abilities</strong> in the game and there are a <strong>12 classes of hero </strong>in the game. With a planned total of at least <strong>25 characters </strong>to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However the player, as the leader of the party, is different. He uses his skills to buff his companions; and uses magic to cast elemental <strong>spells</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/df349de624faee60819e248c144461a9.poster.avif?t=1760778975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/df349de624faee60819e248c144461a9.webm?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/df349de624faee60819e248c144461a9.mp4?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level up</strong> your characters <strong>constellation skill tree</strong> to increase their capability in combat and learn new abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Purchase </strong>new equipment, gain it as <strong>loot </strong>from battles, or <strong>craft </strong>it, to improve the stats of your heroes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/9cb574db4ec23b32a4572b68c5f79fe8.poster.avif?t=1760778975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/9cb574db4ec23b32a4572b68c5f79fe8.webm?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/9cb574db4ec23b32a4572b68c5f79fe8.mp4?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please Wishlist - Coming Soon!</strong></p>",
